cz.syntea.xdef

Interface XDResultSet

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<XDValue>, XDValue, XDValueID
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    XDResultSetAbstract

    public interface XDResultSet
extends XDValue
    Iterator/Map used as context in create mode of X-definition in x-script. This interface can be either an iterator or a map.
